# About

This is a standalone web app which demonstrates how HTTP::BrowserDetect parses
arbitrary UserAgent strings.

The live demonstration site is at https://browserdetect.org

## Deploying Locally

### Without Docker
Clone this repository and:

```bash
cpanm Carton
carton install && carton exec -- morbo bin/app.pl
```

### With Docker

```bash
docker build -t browserdetect .
docker run --rm --volume $PWD:/app -p 3000:3000 browserdetect
```
